AB  - This paper develops further the formal model of tariff-induced capital inflow and immiserization presented by Bhagwati (1973). We set down the necessary and sufficient condition under which immiserization will follow. In addition, it will be shown that the possibility of immiserization depends crucially on the initial amount of foreign capital as well as the rate of corporation tax on foreign capital.
